1.
Run the Verilog simulation by 

  $ ncverilog hw7_1_test.v hw7_1.v +access+r

Or you may use the shell script by

  $ sh ./hw7_1.sh


2.
Files:
  00_README:    This file
  hw7_1.sh:     Shell script to help the simulation
  hw7_1_test.v: Verilog template of test stimulus
  hw7_1.v:      Verilog template of design
